document.title: Portfolio Overview
document.author: Ted Son
document.description: An overview of my portfolio and professional experience

body.raw:
import { Text } from "../components/Text.tsx"; import { Flex } from "../components/Flex.tsx"; Overview ## Experience 💻 As a Web Developer with _4 years of experience_, I have extensive knowledge in the following programming languages:
| Languages | level | | ------------- | ------------ | | 🐍 Python | expert | | 🔴 C | intermediate | | ⛏🧱Cpp | intermediate | | 🟡 JavaScript | expert | | 🔵 TypeScript | intermediate | I also have experience working with various web development stacks, including:
| Stack | | | | ------------------ | ---------------- | -------------------- | | ⚛️ React | 🚀 Next.js | 🔥 Redux | | 🌐 HTML/CSS | 💅 Emotion | 💄 styled-components | | 👕 stitches | 💅 CssInJs | 🎨 Tailwind | | 💧 Liquid/Jinja2 | 💎 Python/Ruby | 📝 Template Language | | 🐚 Shell Scripting | 🐳 Docker | ☁️ AWS | | 🛍️ Shopify | 📦 Amazon SP_API | 🚛 UPS | | 🚀 MDX | | |
# Portfolio 🎨 ## Goselly 🛍️ [Goselly](https://goselly.com) is built using the following technologies: - CMS: `Shopify` - Frontend: `VanillaJS`, `Tailwind`, `Liquid`, `Next.js`, `styled-components` - Other technologies used: `Next.js` ## Amzsaver 🚀 [Amzsaver](https://app.amzsaver.co.kr/) is built using the following technologies: - Backend: `Django` - Frontend: `VanillaJS`, `Tailwind` - Other technologies used: `Next.js`, `Nginx`, `Docker`, `AWS` --- If you're interested in learning more about me, feel free to check out my pages on: - [Notion 📝](https://wobbly-reason-2bc.notion.site/KD-s-Scrap-Paper-b05bafd9d0014f26ad2e288837ba50f1) - [GitHub 🐙](https://github.com/kiduckson) - [LeetCode 🧑‍💻](https://leetcode.com/kiduckson/) Or, if you'd like to get in touch, you can reach me via email at kiduck.son@gmail.com. Thanks for stopping by! 😊

document.author: 손기덕
document.description: An overview of my portfolio and professional experience

body.raw:
import { Text } from "../components/Text.tsx"; import { Flex } from "../components/Flex.tsx"; Overview # Experience 💻 _4년차_ 웹 개발자로 아래의 언어를 자유롭게 사용합니다.
| Languages | level | | ------------- | ------------ | | 🐍 Python | expert | | 🔴 C | intermediate | | ⛏🧱Cpp | intermediate | | 🟡 JavaScript | expert | | 🔵 TypeScript | intermediate | 또한 아래의 기술에 대해 넓은 이해도를 가지고 있습니다.
| Stack | | | | ------------------ | ---------------- | -------------------- | | ⚛️ React | 🚀 Next.js | 🔥 Redux | | 🌐 HTML/CSS | 💅 Emotion | 💄 styled-components | | 👕 stitches | 💅 CssInJs | 🎨 Tailwind | | 💧 Liquid/Jinja2 | 💎 Python/Ruby | 📝 Template Language | | 🐚 Shell Scripting | 🐳 Docker | ☁️ AWS | | 🛍️ Shopify | 📦 Amazon SP_API | 🚛 UPS | | 🚀 MDX | | |
# Portfolio 🎨 ## Goselly 🛍️ [Goselly](https://goselly.com)는 아래의 스택을 이용해 개발하였습니다. - CMS: `Shopify` - Frontend: `VanillaJS`, `Tailwind`, `Liquid`, `Next.js`, `styled-components` - Other technologies used: `Next.js` ## Amzsaver 🚀 [Amzsaver](https://app.amzsaver.co.kr/)는 아래의 스택을 이용해 개발하였습니다. - Backend: `Django` - Frontend: `VanillaJS`, `Tailwind` - Other technologies used: `Next.js`, `Nginx`, `Docker`, `AWS` --- 더 자세한 사항을 원하시면 아래의 링크나 kiduck.son@gmail.com로 연락주세요. - [Notion 📝](https://wobbly-reason-2bc.notion.site/KD-s-Scrap-Paper-b05bafd9d0014f26ad2e288837ba50f1) - [GitHub 🐙](https://github.com/kiduckson) - [LeetCode 🧑‍💻](https://leetcode.com/kiduckson/) 감사합니다.
